{"tid":492602,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"「求助」如何解決波鞋的凹紋","createTime":"2017-12-07T16:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T03:51:58.000Z","uid":116105,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"47d3679f71356bc82832fc4f192925d086a9344e","tid":492602,"uid":116105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:35:24.000Z","msg":"前幾日買左對nmd r2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日終於可以拆包裹，一嘗新鞋既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但著落去發覺鞋既內側有條凹痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟才疏學淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有冇巴打可以指點下小弟點改善依個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/001948_4b4537c6920d46e7b86ee33d359c0b48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F001948_4b4537c6920d46e7b86ee33d359c0b48.jpg&h=acd5d7bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5371265e136aedce3f033890452b24f8eca2bab8","tid":492602,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:38:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfee24cb710fd6816edb3f08cedada87a0440906","tid":492602,"uid":40213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:39:25.000Z","msg":"搵件舊衫 剪塊布出黎<br />\n塞入去塞滿佢"},{"pid":"fdd9f2189bf9a1176f51c137abe8bdf6fb715a78","tid":492602,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:40:26.000Z","msg":"你著多幾次就唔會煩呢d野，你有活動就會有紋，你想無紋就要腳趾唔好屈咁黎行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1099c6f49f668a2883099ca8e49dc0978634ea3a","tid":492602,"uid":53145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:47:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵件舊衫 剪塊布出黎<br />\n塞入去塞滿佢</blockquote>"},{"pid":"